The environment has not yet been created. Run `vagrant up` to
create the environment. If a machine is not created%!(VAGRANT_COMMA) only the
default provider will be shown. So if a provider is not listed%!(VAGRANT_COMMA)
then the machine is not created for that environment.

The VM is running. To stop this VM%!(VAGRANT_COMMA) you can run `vagrant halt` to
shut it down forcefully%!(VAGRANT_COMMA) or you can run `vagrant suspend` to simply
suspend the virtual machine. In either case%!(VAGRANT_COMMA) to restart it again%!(VAGRANT_COMMA)
simply run `vagrant up`.
